# Create classes for showing off correlation_analyze's heatmapping ability
def createClasses(x):
    if x == 'Iris-setosa':
        return 'A'
    elif x == 'Iris-versicolor':
        return 'B'
    else:
        return 'C'
df['Class'] = df['Species'].apply(createClasses)
